===Docudramas===
The Apollo program, or certain missions, have been [[docudrama|dramatized]] in ''[[Apollo 13 (film)|Apollo 13]]'' (1995), ''[[Apollo 11 (1996 film)|Apollo 11]]'' (1996), ''[[From the Earth to the Moon (miniseries)|From the Earth to the Moon]]'' (1998), ''[[The Dish]]'' (2000), ''[[Space Race (TV series)|Space Race]]'' (2005), ''[[Moonshot (film)|Moonshot]]'' (2009), and ''[[First Man (film)|First Man]]'' (2018).

===Fictional===
The Apollo program has been the focus of several works of fiction, including:
*''[[Apollo 18 (film)|Apollo 18]]'' (2011): A [[Horror film|horror]] movie which was released in 2011 to negative reviews.
*''[[For All Mankind (TV series)|For All Mankind]]'' (2019): A TV series which debuted in 2019.

